title: [Sylvarraend Road]
description: Stern fences continue to line the path and, on one side, a small gopher lies curled up under the moonlit sky.  The light sound of waves lapping against the shore can be heard from this distance.
Stern fences continue to line the path and, on one side, a small gopher basks in the sun while nibbling a carrot.  The light sound of waves lapping against the shore can be heard from this distance.
